snippet.textDisplay:
well i have some contradictory comment here for this video. Indeed Ar rehman is an excellent composer and there are no doubts about it.. but this song and video truly feels like he is being inspired from Yanni and karunesh. its kind of the blend of both. and tibetan music is for peace lovers who truly understand the depth of silence . i did not like the fusion of those tibetan strings with the rest of the song.. Listen to karunesh songs and you will feel the immense feeling of tobetan music. 
again i am not here to offend anyone or being rude. i just wanted to present my views.
